613
00:56:28,580 --> 00:56:30,172
Mr. Jennings, I'm Stone.

614
00:56:30,260 --> 00:56:32,774
Were you able to get the files I requested?

615
00:56:33,860 --> 00:56:36,658
This guy's already committed
two acts of sabotage.

616
00:56:36,980 --> 00:56:39,972
JENNINGS: Mr. MacGruder will be going
along with you as liaison.

617
00:56:40,060 --> 00:56:41,891
