618
00:56:42,100 --> 00:56:43,818
...he'll be reporting to me.

619
00:56:43,900 --> 00:56:45,413
JENNINGS: Understood?

620
00:56:45,780 --> 00:56:46,849
Understood.

621
00:56:46,940 --> 00:56:49,852
If there's no new information,
we'll get on with the search.

622
00:56:49,940 --> 00:56:53,615
We've got quite a sophisticated
little listening post set up inside.

623
00:56:54,780 --> 00:56:56,213
We'll find your man.

624
00:56:56,340 --> 00:56:58,456
That brings us to another question.

625
00:57:03,060 --> 00:57:05,016
How do you want him delivered?

626
00:57:09,780 --> 00:57:10,849
I see.

627
00:57:15,700 --> 00:57:17,975
[Dramatic instrumental music]

628
00:57:39,700 --> 00:57:40,735
Hey, brother.

629
00:57:40,820 --> 00:57:41,969
Hey, brother.

630
00:57:42,940 --> 00:57:45,977
