00:58:22,140 --> 00:58:24,779
Or they'll broker the space
to another company.

646
00:58:25,620 --> 00:58:26,689
Clever.

647
00:58:27,420 --> 00:58:31,811
This is just one of the many little activities
that Jennings uses to...

648
00:58:33,140 --> 00:58:36,337
...finance Aegis-1 and the rest
of his dog-shit empire.

649
00:58:39,220 --> 00:58:40,892
lt's like l always say...

650
00:58:41,420 --> 00:58:42,694
...we gotta blow it...

651
00:58:42,780 --> 00:58:44,611
...and we gotta blow it now.

652
00:58:50,380 --> 00:58:52,848
MASU: Blowing up Aegis-1 is not
the answer.

653
00:58:52,940 --> 00:58:54,817
There are enough dead bodies.

654
00:58:55,060 --> 00:58:56,812
Let's leave it to the authorities.

655
00:58:56,900 --> 00:58:58,856
I know the press. Let's contact the press.

656
00:58:58,940 --> 00:59:01,090
Haven't you learned anything
from my father?

657
00:59:01,180 --> 00:59:03,250
What do you want me to learn, Masu?

658
00:59:04,020 --> 00:59:08,775
Do you really think that this hocus-pocus
spirit stuff is gonna help us now?

659
00:59:09,340 --> 00:59:12,730
What do you think, an angel will
