668
00:59:37,220 --> 00:59:39,688
...so that Jennings can't fuck you
and your people...

669
00:59:39,780 --> 00:59:42,135
...out of your land
and your way of life forever.

670
00:59:42,220 --> 00:59:44,495
See, I loved the spirit world
and your father.

671
00:59:44,580 --> 00:59:46,059
But it doesn't matter right now.

672
00:59:46,140 --> 00:59:49,416
What really matters is the cold,
hard reality of this world.

673
00:59:49,540 --> 00:59:51,292
That's what we've gotta deal with.

674
00:59:51,380 --> 00:59:53,496
I didn't want to resort to violence.

675
00:59:53,700 --> 00:59:57,215
I don't have a choice and I'm not taking
any chances this time...

676
00:59:57,500 --> 00:59:58,933
...because I can't.

677
01:00:07,700 --> 01:00:09,850
I'll go into the mountains
over the back ridge.

