01:01:07,140 --> 01:01:09,017
Yes, we are aware. So what?

689
01:01:09,100 --> 01:01:11,773
So what was he doing?
What's his military record?

690
01:01:11,860 --> 01:01:14,932
Where in the hell did he receive
his EOD training at?

691
01:01:15,140 --> 01:01:17,734
We couldn't access that information
at the time.

692
01:01:17,820 --> 01:01:20,618
And now we don't feel
it's germane to his capture.

693
01:01:20,860 --> 01:01:22,373
What do you got on the screen?

694
01:01:22,460 --> 01:01:24,132
SPINKS: Nothing yet, sir.

695
01:01:31,220 --> 01:01:34,417
Our man in DC finds nothing
on this guy before 1987.

696
01:01:34,820 --> 01:01:37,095
Which means either he was born
fully grown...

697
01:01:37,180 --> 01:01:38,818
...or his background is so secret...

698
01:01:38,900 --> 01:01:41,778
