01:06:14,460 --> 01:06:15,415
STONE: There he is.

735
01:06:15,500 --> 01:06:17,377
We've got him now. Let's go.

736
01:06:27,660 --> 01:06:29,537
STONE: Hold it up.

737
01:06:41,260 --> 01:06:44,138
COLLINS: Looks like he kept
to the trail after he set it.

738
01:06:44,220 --> 01:06:46,495
You had me spooked on the chopper
