Fuck you.

743
01:07:01,940 --> 01:07:02,770
Hold it up!

744
01:07:02,860 --> 01:07:04,054
Wait a minute!

745
01:07:07,340 --> 01:07:09,058
Son of a bitch, cease fire!

746
01:07:09,460 --> 01:07:11,291
What the hell are you doing?

