...that are all accumulative poisons.

1001
01:30:14,700 --> 01:30:18,136
These poisons kill us slowly,
even when we see no effect.

1002
01:30:18,700 --> 01:30:22,010
How many of us would've believed
if we were told 20 years ago...

1003
01:30:22,100 --> 01:30:25,888
...that on a certain day we wouldn't be able
to see 50 feet in front of us...

1004
01:30:25,980 --> 01:30:28,369
...that we wouldn't be able
to take a deep breath...

1005
01:30:28,460 --> 01:30:31,372
...because the air would be a mass
ofpoisonous gas.

1006
01:30:31,540 --> 01:30:33,610
That we couldn't drink out of our faucets...

1007
01:30:33,700 --> 01:30:36,294
...that we'd have to buy water
out of bottles.

1008
01:30:36,740 --> 01:30:40,016
Our most common and God-given rights
have been taken away from us.

1009
01:30:40,100 --> 01:30:41,294
Unfortunately...

1010
01:30:41,380 --> 01:30:45,055
...the reality of our lives is so grim
that nobody wants to hear it.

1011
01:30:45,180 --> 01:30:47,091
I've been asked what we can do.

1012
01:30:47,620 --> 01:30:51,818
l think we need a responsible body
ofpeople that can actually represent us...

1013
01:30:51,900 --> 01:30:53,379
...rather than big business.

1014
01:30:53,460 --> 01:30:55,291
This body ofpeople must not allow...

1015
01:30:55,380 --> 01:30:59,692
...the introduction of anything into our
environment that is not biodegradable...

1016
01:31:00,300 --> 01:31:03,372
...or able to be chemically neutralized
upon production.

1017
01:31:04,020 --> 01:31:08,332
Finally, as long as there's profit to be made
from the polluting of our earth...

1018
01:31:08,500 --> 01:31:11,970
...companies and individuals will continue
to do what they want.

1019
01:31:12,540 --> 01:31:16,294
We have to force these companies
to operate safely and responsibly...

1020
01:31:16,580 --> 01:31:20,368
...with all our best interests in mind,
so that when they don't...

1021
01:31:20,540 --> 01:31:25,011
...we can take back our resources and our
hearts and our minds, and do what's right.

1022
01:31:26,020 --> 01:31:27,214
