Kompasla, great spirit, bless the people...

1024
01:31:31,980 --> 01:31:35,211
...all the grandmas, all the grandpas,
and the little ones.

1025
01:31:35,700 --> 01:31:37,611
We have the four directions...

1026
01:31:37,740 --> 01:31:39,412
...and l want to bless...

1027
01:31:39,700 --> 01:31:43,739
...the future generation
and the Indian nation, our people...

1028
01:31:44,060 --> 01:31:45,652
...to be strong again.

1029
01:31:45,900 --> 01:31:47,219
Spotted Eagle...

1030
